{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "002c91bd-51dd-4315-9946-96c557a3e24a", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/002c91bd-51dd-4315-9946-96c557a3e24a@3.pkg/1772597602886/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597603636", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/002c91bd-51dd-4315-9946-96c557a3e24a@3.pkg/1772597602886/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597603636"}, "identifier": "002c91bd-51dd-4315-9946-96c557a3e24a", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p>本题考查国家主席的职权。材料中国家主席根据全国人民代表大会常务委员会的决定,任免外交部部长,这是行使任免权的表现,C正确。ABD在材料中没有体现,排除。</p>\n"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<p>2023年7月25日,中华人民共和国主席习近平根据第十四届全国人民代表大会常务委员会第四次会议的决定,免去秦刚兼任的外交部部长职务；任命王毅为外交部部长。这表明国家主席行使（ &nbsp;&nbsp;）</p>\n", "title": "2023年7月25日,中华人民共和国主席习近平根据第十四届全国人民代表大会常务委员会第四次会议的决定,免去秦刚兼任的外交部部长职务；任命王毅为外交部部长。这表明国家主席行使（   ）", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["C"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/002c91bd-51dd-4315-9946-96c557a3e24a@3.pkg/item.json?v=1754813458351", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_i